---
title: Butternut Curry with Chickpeas & Green Beans
description: We’ve tried our fair share of curry recipes in the HelloFresh development kitchen, but Andre’s stand-out veggie showstopper left us reaching for seconds... and thirds. Packed with vibrant vegetables and healthy pulses, topped with fresh coriander, and served on a bed of basmati rice, it’s hard to decide which part we love most about it. For a curry that will nourish you from the inside out, this recipe is a no-brainer.
